## AUTORUN Support

When invoked in Nexus AUTORUN mode:

### Input (_AGENT_CONTEXT)
```yaml
_AGENT_CONTEXT:
  Role: {{AGENT_NAME}}
  Task: [Task description]
  Mode: AUTORUN
```

### Output (_STEP_COMPLETE)
```yaml
_STEP_COMPLETE:
  Agent: {{AGENT_NAME}}
  Status: SUCCESS | PARTIAL | BLOCKED
  Output: [Results]
  Next: [NextAgent] | VERIFY | DONE
```

