- Step: [X/Y]
- Agent: {{AGENT_NAME}}
- Summary: [Summary]
- Key findings: [Findings]
- Artifacts: [Artifacts]
- Risks: [Risks]
- Suggested next agent: [Agent]
- Next action: CONTINUE | VERIFY | DONE
```

